data.description: Discover this 4-bed, 3-bath gem in SE Omaha, near South Omaha's vibrant community. At 4116 M Street, this home blends suburban peace with city access. It features a welcoming living room, modern kitchen, and spacious bedrooms, including a master suite and don't forget the bonus rooms in the basement! The finished basement offers potential for a second kitchen, ideal for rental or dual living. With a cozy backyard and patio, it's perfect for family gatherings. Located near I-80 and US-75, downtown Omaha and attractions like the Henry Doorly Zoo are easily accessible. A prime spot with both comfort and investment potential awaits you!
